title: Cumulative Index to Nursing Literature
additional-note: Some volumes were published in revised editions that may still have active copyrights.  For example, the first volume, covering 1956-1960, was published in a second edition in 1964.  That edition has a 1964 copyright notice, and that copyright, like other copyrights from 1964 and later, automatically renewed.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Pete Sullivan for copyright research on this title.
